<h2 class="titleHead" id="toward-a-theory-of-organisms-three-founding-principles-in-search-of-a-useful-integration">Toward a theory of organisms: Three founding principles in search of a useful integration</h2>
<p class="indent author" style="text-align:center">Ana M. Soto, Giuseppe Longo, Paul-Antoine Miquel, Maël Montévil, Matteo Mossio, Nicole Perret, Arnaud Pocheville and Carlos Sonnenschein</p>
<p class="author"> </p>
